ygData.messageBody:
Tina,
Thanks for the response about different characters and their strengths.
I have tried a Ranger, and I loved the tracking ability! But I wanted
to try more magic so I am now going with my druid.
I can tell from your list of characters that you like the casters
classes best. And wow, you have some high levels going too. I can't
wait to get to lvl 9. I can't imagine lvl 54!!
I hope the ex-boyfriend guild situation works out.
